item.title: Akyut - Skyward Bound
item.dc:creator: iammane
item.description:
I like it man. Definitely a different style but I think it fits just fine. Not every song should be 100% in the face anyway nice to break up the energy. Still has your sound on it I believe so it’s not like “whodafuq wrote this?” lol
